
<div class="cta-1">
  <div class="container">
      <div class="row text-center white">
      <h1 class="cta-title">MeowMates</h1>
      <p class="cta-sub-title">Find your purrrfect cat today!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div id="service" class="section-padding">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="page-title text-center">
        <h1>Our Service</h1>
        <p>MeowMates is a pet adoption site.<br>Here you can browse for pets and get a good idea for who they are before you adopt.</p>
        <hr class="pg-titl-bdr-btm"></hr>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="service-box">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-picture-o"></i></div>
          <div class="service-text">
            <h3>Create your Pets Profile</h3>
            <p>Create a profile, upload pics and more</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="service-box">
          <div class="service-icon">
            <i class="fa fa fa-code"></i></div>
          <div class="service-text">
            <h3>Meet other Pets</h3>
            <p>Meet other pets. Browse through profiles to find the purrfect pet.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <div class="service-box">
          <div class="service-icon"><i class="fa fa-diamond"></i></div>
          <div class="service-text">
            <h3>Adopt!</h3>
            <p>Once you find a pet, click the Adopt, button and we will send a notification to the owner.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <div id="newsfeed" class="col-lg-12">
    <h4><%= fa_icon "newspaper-o" %> Check out some of the cats posted</h4>
    <div>
      <%= render 'shared/animal_gallery', animal: @animals %>
    </div>
  </div>


</div>
